structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 352, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1988. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 340, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1986.
